title: Capitol Reef National Park: Partners
body: Partners       To contact the park, please dial (435) 425-3791. You will be transferred to our voice mail system, which will then provide instructions on contacting the staff member or division you would like to reach. Capitol Reef Natural History Association ext. 4107 Shirley Torgerson, Executive Director, Natural History Association ext. 4108 Diana Elmer, Operations Specialist, Natural History Association ext. 4106 Natural History Association Bookstore
